import React from 'react';
import {  View, Text, StyleSheet } from 'react-native';

const Layout = () => {
    return (
        <View style={{flexDirection: 'row', justifyContent: 'center'}}>

            <View style={{
            height: 70,
            padding:10,
            width: '25%',
            shadowColor: '#000',
            shadowOpacity:0.2,
            shadowRadius:1,
            backgroundColor:'#f6d743',
            borderRadius:10
            }}>
            <Text style={{ textAlign: 'center', fontWeight: 'bold'}}>Positif</Text>
            </View>

            <View style={{
            height: 70,
            padding:10,
            marginLeft: '5%',
            width: '25%',
            shadowColor: '#000',
            shadowOpacity:0.2,
            shadowRadius:1,
            backgroundColor:'#42e6a4',
            borderRadius:10
            }}>
            <Text style={{ textAlign: 'center', fontWeight: 'bold'}}>Sembuh</Text>
            </View>

            <View style={{ 
            height: 70,
            padding:10,
            marginBottom:0,
            marginLeft: '5%',
            width: '25%',
            shadowColor: '#000',
            shadowOpacity:0.2,
            shadowRadius:1,
            backgroundColor:'#eb4559',
            borderRadius:10
             }}>
            <Text style={{ textAlign: 'center', fontWeight: 'bold'}}>Meninggal</Text>
            </View>


        </View>
    )


};

export default Layout;
